name: EZ-Bar Skullcrushers
description: 1. Using an EZ-bar and a bench lay with your back on the bench and grasp the bar with an overhand grip just inside shoulder width 2. Hold the bar with your arms straight out above your body 3. Without moving your upper arms bend your elbows to lower the bar until the weight is just at or just behind your forehead 4. Extend the elbows lifting the weight back to the start position without moving your upper arms 5. Repeat for desired reps
